  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The proposed study aims to investigate the feasibility, effectiveness, and perceived benefit
      of a hatha yoga intervention for patients with irritable bowel syndrome (IBS) compared to
      nutrition counselling. Further, the potential of both interventions to influence the gut
      microbiome will be inquired.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
